            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a Fe3O4-Fe2O3 wide light band absorption heterojunction photoanode and a preparation method thereof. The preparation method comprises the following steps: firstly, carrying out hydrophilic treatment on FTO glass, putting (NH4) 2Fe (SO4) 2.6 H2O, CH3COONa. 3H2O and Na2SO4 into deionized water, uniformly stirring, putting into a reaction kettle, vertically putting the treated FTO glass into the reaction kettle, and carrying out high-temperature reaction; and cleaning and drying. The Fe3O4/Fe2O3 heterojunction is prepared by adopting a simple one-step hydrothermal synthesis method, and the method is simple and novel; the prepared Fe3O4/Fe2O3 heterojunction has the uniform morphology of combining nanosheets and micro-cone pyramids, has larger specific surface area and active sites, and can absorb visible light and near-infrared light at the same time; the II-type pn heterojunction increases the photoelectrocatalytic activity and can be used as a photoanode for photocatalytic electrolysis of water to generate clean energy hydrogen."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本案涉及一种Fe3O4‑Fe2O3宽光带吸收异质结光阳极及其制备方法，首先亲水处理FTO玻璃，将(NH4)2Fe(SO4)2·6H2O、CH3COONa·3H2O和Na2SO4置于去离子水中，搅拌均匀，置于反应釜中，将处理后的FTO玻璃垂直放入反应釜中，进行高温反应；清洗干净后干燥即得。本发明采用简单的一步水热合成法制备得到了Fe3O4/Fe2O3异质结，方法简单新颖；制得的Fe3O4/Fe2O3异质结具有均匀的纳米片与微锥金字塔结合的形貌，拥有更大的比表面积和活性位点，能够同时吸收可见和近红外光；Ⅱ型的pn异质结增加了光电催化活性，可作为光阳极光催化电解水产生清洁能源氢气。"
                }
            ]
